  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EFPTO allows full-time, salaried exempt employees to take paid time off for vacation, personal needs, or illness without annual accruals. Requests must be pre-approved, and extended absences require coverage planning. Misuse may result in corrective action. This policy is designed to promote flexibility and work-life balance while ensuring business continuity.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
